@host = http://localhost:5029

### ========== HEALTH ==========

GET {{host}}/api/health
Accept: application/json

### ========== SPACES ==========

### Listar todos os espacos
GET {{host}}/api/spaces
Accept: application/json

### Criar espaco
POST {{host}}/api/spaces
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Espaco de Teste",
  "description": "Descricao do espaco de teste"
}

### Buscar espaco por ID
GET {{host}}/api/spaces/1
Accept: application/json

### Atualizar espaco
PUT {{host}}/api/spaces/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Espaco Atualizado",
  "description": "Descricao atualizada"
}

### Deletar espaco (soft delete)
DELETE {{host}}/api/spaces/1

### ========== PAGES ==========

### Listar paginas de um espaco
GET {{host}}/api/pages?spaceId=1
Accept: application/json

### Criar pagina
POST {{host}}/api/pages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Pagina de Teste",
  "description": "Descricao da pagina",
  "content": "{\"type\":\"doc\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Hello World\"}]}]}",
  "sortOrder": 0,
  "spaceId": 1
}

### Buscar pagina por ID
GET {{host}}/api/pages/1
Accept: application/json

### Atualizar pagina
PUT {{host}}/api/pages/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Pagina Atualizada",
  "description": "Descricao atualizada",
  "content": "{\"type\":\"doc\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Conteudo atualizado\"}]}]}",
  "sortOrder": 1
}

### Deletar pagina (soft delete)
DELETE {{host}}/api/pages/1

### Criar pagina com espaco inexistente (deve retornar 404)
POST {{host}}/api/pages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Pagina Invalida",
  "sortOrder": 0,
  "spaceId": 9999
}

### ========== TESTES DE VALIDACAO ==========

### Criar espaco sem titulo (deve retornar 400)
POST {{host}}/api/spaces
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "",
  "description": "Sem titulo"
}
